WEBVTT

00:00.341 --> 00:01.457
My name is John.

00:02.111 --> 00:03.687
I am a high school student.

00:04.646 --> 00:07.327
I like to read books and write stories.

00:08.299 --> 00:10.409
I want to study education in college.

00:11.017 --> 00:13.045
My dream is to become a teacher.

00:13.909 --> 00:15.744
I want to teach many students...

00:16.121 --> 00:17.615
...and work in different schools.

00:18.560 --> 00:21.174
I want to help children achieve their dreams.

00:21.898 --> 00:24.748
Someday, I hope to write books for children.

